What is Rest Assured?
Rest Assured is a Java library used to test APIs!

What is BDD?
BDD is a branch of Test Driven Development. BDD uses human readable description of software user requirements

Scenario:
Creating an Employee
Given a request is prepared to create an Employee
When a Post call is made to create that Employee
Then the status code for creating an employee is 201
AND the employee is created

Given() you pass the request headers, query and path parameters, body, cookies
When() When marks the promise of your scenario, e.g When you get/post/put
Then() Your assert and matcher condition are written here

Hamcrest library is what we use to perform assertions
equalTo
allof
anyofhasToString

